OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1775049067
OL,3,CPolice give High Court apology to
OL,4,Cfamily of loyalist paramilitary murder
OL,5,Cvictim
OL,7,FPolice have issued a High Court
OL,8,Fapology to the family of a loyalist
OL,9,Fparamilitary murder victim for
OL,10,F"inadequacies" in the investigation
OL,11,Finto his death.
OL,13,FUndisclosed damages also form part of
OL,14,Fa settlement announced on Tuesday in
OL,15,Fan action brought by the mother of
OL,16,FFergal McCusker, her lawyer said.
OL,18,FMr McCusker was shot dead by the LVF
OL,19,Fin Maghera, Co Londonderry as he made
OL,20,Fhis way home from a night out in
OL,21,FJanuary 1998.
OL,26,@rD@AOUrD@NO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/9
