FL,448,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1775049067
OL,3,CPolice give High Court apology to
OL,4,Cfamily of loyalist paramilitary murder
OL,5,Cvictim
OL,7,FThe 28-year-old victim had just
OL,8,Freturned to Northern Ireland from the
OL,9,FUnited States a short time before he
OL,10,Fwas abducted and killed.
OL,12,FNo-one has ever been prosecuted for
OL,13,Fthe murder.
OL,15,FThe family have held concerns about
OL,16,Fthe Royal Ulster Constabulary
OL,17,Finvestigation and the potential
OL,18,Finvolvement of state agents.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/9
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
