OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,448,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1775049067
OL,3,CPolice give High Court apology to
OL,4,Cfamily of loyalist paramilitary murder
OL,5,Cvictim
OL,7,FAn inquest into the killing was halted
OL,8,Fin 2024 amid issues around information
OL,9,Fbeing withheld on grounds of security.
OL,11,FMr McCusker's mother, Christina, sued
OL,12,Fthe police for alleged negligence and
OL,13,Fmisfeasance in public office.
OL,15,FIn court on Tuesday, it was confirmed
OL,16,Fthat negotiations have led to a
OL,17,Fsettlement in her action against the
OL,18,FPolice Service of Northern Ireland
OL,19,F(PSNI).
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/9
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,448,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1775049067
OL,3,CPolice give High Court apology to
OL,4,Cfamily of loyalist paramilitary murder
OL,5,Cvictim
OL,7,FCounsel for Mrs McCusker, Des Fahy KC,
OL,8,Fread out an agreed statement part of
OL,9,Fthe resolution.
OL,11,F"The PSNI does not admit liability but
OL,12,Frecognises that aspects of the
OL,13,Finvestigation fell below expected
OL,14,Fstandards," Mr Fahy said.
OL,16,F"The PSNI wishes to apologise to the
OL,17,FMcCusker family for the inadequacies
OL,18,Fin the RUC investigation."
OL,26,@sD@AOUvD@KO]xD@AOUzD@ZO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/9
