PN,44705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1775049067
OL,3,CPolice give High Court apology to
OL,4,Cfamily of loyalist paramilitary murder
OL,5,Cvictim
OL,7,FPolice also acknowledged both the deep
OL,8,Fand lasting grief suffered by the
OL,9,Ffamily, and how the shortcomings had
OL,10,Fcaused additional distress.
OL,12,FMr Justice Rooney was told the force
OL,13,F"affirms its commitment to learning
OL,14,Ffrom such cases in order to strengthen
OL,15,Fpublic confidence in the justice
OL,16,Fsystem".
OL,26,@uD@AOUxD@GO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/9
