OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,448,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1775049067
OL,3,CPolice give High Court apology to
OL,4,Cfamily of loyalist paramilitary murder
OL,5,Cvictim
OL,7,FCounsel added: "The PSNI recognises
OL,8,Fthat reconciliation is an ongoing
OL,9,Fsocietal process and affirms its
OL,10,Fbroader institutional responsibility
OL,11,Fto uphold the values of fairness,
OL,12,Ftransparency and accountability in its
OL,13,Fwork."
OL,15,FCommending both sides for reaching a
OL,16,Fsettlement, the judge described it as
OL,17,Fan example of how civil claims can
OL,18,Fhelp bring closure in such tragic
OL,19,Fcases.
OL,26,@oD@POUuD@FO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/9
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,448,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44707
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1775049067
OL,3,CPolice give High Court apology to
OL,4,Cfamily of loyalist paramilitary murder
OL,5,Cvictim
OL,7,FMrs McCusker's solicitor, Padraig O
OL,8,FMuirigh, announced later that
OL,9,Fundisclosed damages form part of the
OL,10,Fresolution.
OL,12,F"I can confirm that the settlement is
OL,13,Fsignificant and our client is
OL,14,Fsatisfied with the outcome of this
OL,15,Flitigation," he said.
OL,17,F"The McCusker family have fought
OL,18,Ftirelessly to expose the inadequacies
OL,19,Fin the police investigation in the 28
OL,20,Fyears since his death.
OL,26,@tD@AOUwD@LO]yD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G7/9
