CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1775049067
OL,3,CPolice give High Court apology to
OL,4,Cfamily of loyalist paramilitary murder
OL,5,Cvictim
OL,7,F"Christina McCusker has been treated
OL,8,Fdisgracefully by those who were tasked
OL,9,Fto investigate her son's murder.
OL,11,F"She should not have been placed in
OL,12,Fthe position of having to pursue
OL,13,Flengthy and protracted legal
OL,14,Fproceedings to get to this point."
